{"tid":1184782,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國資金沽出中国国企股票或中国股票的可能結果","createTime":"2019-06-04T00:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T13:52:49.000Z","uid":76310,"like":97,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"de3dafda1162a1fb7adfd9004cb153b72414c178","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"The Trump Dump: war-gaming the next move against China<br />\n<br />\n侵侵發文表示，為什麼用美國人民金錢去投資沒有透明度獨裁国家政體的股票？為什麼用美國人民的金錢和基金去投資獨裁政權，為什麼投資中国支持中国獨裁的力量<br />\n言下之意，美國可能在不久將來要求美國機構，美國基金沽清中国国企或中国股票"},{"pid":"09e1814d54a2061f3a585a13803b351b2e074576","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:47:59.000Z","msg":"美國日前對俄羅斯2016年干預大選向對方施加嚴厲制裁，多家俄企高層被列入名單，包括俄鋁非執行董事歐柏嘉（Oleg Deripaska），俄鋁指制裁或導致部分信貸技術性違約<br />\n<br />\n俄鋁非執董歐柏嘉被列入制裁名單<br />\n<br />\n俄鋁其後再被評級機構穆迪及惠譽撤銷所有評級，公司近日再發通告表示，就可能出售Norilsk Nickel交易尋求股東授權，並不符合公司及股東整體最佳利益，股價今日再插逾三成，已近全日低位1.42元收市，一周以來累挫近7成，市值蒸發489億元，比期內在俄羅斯上市的股份（United Company RUSAL Plc）跌43%還要多。<br />\n<br />\n俄鋁遭外資拋售，有外資行如渣打香港指基於合規理由，已暫停俄鋁買入交易，沽出則不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是當日俄鋁的下場<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SPpou5x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSPpou5x.png&h=96d6c79f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"844d63f94f9be014af30c2c9eb28cded78d18bf4","tid":1184782,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個問題 問返前任班撚屌..."},{"pid":"0ac62df7c9d720468a19499c50fa8354e47a516c","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:53:17.000Z","msg":"現在一切未成真<br />\n就算成真，草擬行政政令需時<br />\n如果成真，個人覺得有二個結果<br />\n1。美國基金不想一下子沽出，每日一點點沽出，變成陰跌局面<br />\n2。美國基金一下沽晒，暴挫<br />\n<br />\n中国應該會護盤，但只是托住指數<br />\n其他股票成災"},{"pid":"ce20dfcb6ba0de8a76e8f02bfda3182dd8229fbc","tid":1184782,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"共d外資產囉<br />\n又唔係未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b319993318233b3b89899eee14bae1a5720fde2d","tid":1184782,"uid":13663,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"0ac62df7c9d720468a19499c50fa8354e47a516c","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:53:17.000Z","msg":"現在一切未成真<br />\n就算成真，草擬行政政令需時<br />\n如果成真，個人覺得有二個結果<br />\n1。美國基金不想一下子沽出，每日一點點沽出，變成陰跌局面<br />\n2。美國基金一下沽晒，暴挫<br />\n<br />\n中国應該會護盤，但只是托住指數<br />\n其他股票成災"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:55:26.000Z","msg":"美資走得 全世界都走<br />\n仲有人玩中資咩"},{"pid":"a710d9803eb0aa73c2b7ef68625f77eac8a51a93","tid":1184782,"uid":105219,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"點解David Webb話會變左侵侵話呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource please"},{"pid":"748cd18aa2838b07408f22fc97c71c629243cc48","tid":1184782,"uid":44171,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:59:39.000Z","msg":"睇下早2，3年前有紀錄片叫中國騙局, 已經講晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23917b9655b00e50f19f301421e5db662049949d","tid":1184782,"uid":5549,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"傻西雜種仲想出反制美國措施，簡直係不自量力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6057e523b429b0ce5b77165830e86cc3d5c066ac","tid":1184782,"uid":5178,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:02:30.000Z","msg":"中國都要沽美債!"},{"pid":"d97bbf0a088c5f2bb00262cfd51a42d0978b270a","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://webb-site.com/articles/trumpdump.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com%2Farticles%2Ftrumpdump.asp&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eokw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=f02572d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com/articles/trumpdump.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n美國資金天文數字<br />\n中港可以接多少？"},{"pid":"49d760668b42c72f6af0858922f9e2d0b5ad2df1","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"獨立股評人David Webb在最新網誌中預期，美國總統特朗普會使用外國資產管控辦公室(OFAC)權力，推動對中國資本制裁，<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb指，美國會發現千億計美元的退休基金、互惠基金、基金等投資中國、香港及美國上市中資企業的股票及債券，當中不少為國營或受中國政府保護。富達、貝萊德及Capital Group等全球最大資產管理公司均以美國為總部，該等公司亦管理非美國人資產，同樣投資中國證券。但中國對內資投資境外設嚴格資本限制。<br />\n<br />\n相關內容人行陳雨露：將擇機推股權融資支持工具<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb認為，當中美耗盡關稅工具後，不會對特朗普實施資本制裁及逼使美國退休基金沽售中國股債感到意外，OFAC的力量已在去年4月俄鋁(<a href=\"http://00486.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00486.HK&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eokw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=1f3c572e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00486.HK</a>) -0.100 (-3.472%) 沽空 $34.66萬; 比率 3.125% 被制裁時反映。他認為，若美國財政部在經濟戰中未考慮有關選項，會令人感到意外，且有關措施或會在下一輪對中國貨品關稅實施後或同時推出，先下令美國退休基金退出所有國企，如銀行股、石油及石化股，其後轉向針對設有黨組織的私人企業。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb指，有關沽售除對股價造成大規模損傷外，對美國基金的影響相對有限，因他們可作其他投資。(fc/u)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2019-06-03 16:25。)"},{"pid":"3aa93d657ac7f610a53db0199afc98a29bda29a5","tid":1184782,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:24:16.000Z","msg":"仆街了，支共無得再無限融資美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80457d6f6bd7c17f6907b5feab847316f854bd0a","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:24:19.000Z","msg":"現在政策未出台<br />\n當然唔一定出台<br />\n但如果一出台，俄鋁為例子，最差情況，可以快速無左2/3"},{"pid":"d271791391f852db08fddca4e31c7f0bb6a84105","tid":1184782,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fe4ae5e6ae4e5b4f03c131148e48a3cdbc0e6011","tid":1184782,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"using the US Treasury's Office of Foreign Assets Control (OFAC). According to its web site:<br />\n&quot;[OFAC] administers and enforces economic and trade sanctions based on US foreign policy and national security goals against targeted foreign countries and regimes, terrorists, international narcotics traffickers, those engaged in activities related to the proliferation of weapons of mass destruction, and other threats to the national security, foreign policy or economy of the United States.&quot;<br />\nOFAC's powers were demonstrated in Apr-2018 when it ordered US Persons to divest, and stop dealing with, Russian aluminium firm United Company Rusal plc, on the grounds that it was controlled by a man who is close to the Russian regime. OFAC cited the regime's occupation of Crimea, support of President Assad's regime in Syria, and attempts to subvert Western democracies. US Persons were ordered to divest Rusal within a month. The HK-listed shares plunged, and for a while it was even impossible to get a stock price from US-based information providers, who were prohibited from dealing with the firm. Index-providers and credit-ratings agencies also had to drop coverage. Eventually the sanctions were lifted following a rearrangement of directors and shareholdings."},{"pid":"079c6620a7d51317a048cef6f656c78df04982a7","tid":1184782,"uid":174767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"沽得幾多。。5%就要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0850532b026fbeba993a9b2637ec12600a1c187e","tid":1184782,"uid":43173,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"079c6620a7d51317a048cef6f656c78df04982a7","tid":1184782,"uid":174767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"沽得幾多。。5%就要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"應該可以連續幾個星期開市5分鐘"},{"pid":"151aec9b1b60d8c5ee7b5897377b40e2bc9d3eb1","tid":1184782,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0850532b026fbeba993a9b2637ec12600a1c187e","tid":1184782,"uid":43173,"like":